These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey, swimming, cricket, baseball
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, raspberry, pomegranate, pineapple, kale
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
5. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
7. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | swimming | surfing | baseball | cricket |
| Food   | kale    | cabbage | pomegranate     | pineapple       | raspberry  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, chestnut, light-blue, amber, emerald
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, tulip, sunflower, azalea
1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Color      | chestnut | light-blue | ebony | amber | emerald |
| Flower   | tulip  | sunflower   | poppy       | aconite    | azalea   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, september, march, july, october
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, mirinda, milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday        | march | july | september | april | october |
| Beverage   | fanta  | tea      | hot-chocolate | mirinda | milk      |

