.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different games are played: billiard, bridge, whist, snooker, go
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, sprite, water, tea
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Game   | snooker    | billiard        | whist | bridge | go |
| Beverage     | coffee | water | tea  | milk   | sprite |

