.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, bike, roller, airplane, scooter
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, water, soy-milk, tea, milk
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person drinking water is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person drinking milk is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Transport    | roller   | bus     | bike   | airplane         | scooter |
| Beverage   | cola | tea | soy-milk | milk | water     |

