.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, october, december, june, february
There 5 different types of food: plum, eggplant, apple, watermelon, onion
1. the person eating watermelon is in the middle##1
2. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating apple is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Birthday       | june   | december   | october | february | august |
| Food   | eggplant | apple | watermelon   | onion | plum       |

