.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, chess, camping, drawing, traveling
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, documentary, romance, comedy, disaster
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
6. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby     | chess   | camping  | traveling      | sudoku | drawing     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | romance | documentary | western   | disaster |

