.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, fanta
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, fuchsia, blue, lavender, purple
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | juice       | fanta | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    |
| Color   | lavender   | purple | blue  | fuchsia     | grey |

