.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, coach, teacher, architect, dressmaker
5 different games are played: domino, backgammon, snooker, scrabble, canasta
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the teacher is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the coach is on the far right##1
4. the architect is on the far left##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the dressmaker is the person playing backgammon##1
7. the architect is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Job         | architect | nurse | teacher | dressmaker | coach |
| Game   | snooker       | scrabble   | canasta         | backgammon   | domino   |

