.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
5 different games are played: scrabble, poker, bridge, chess, billiard
The people have 5 different hobbies: photography, board-games, gardening, traveling, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Game   | billiard | chess | poker | bridge | scrabble |
| Hobby           | dancing      | board-games    | traveling  | photography     | gardening     |

