.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, poppy, rose, bellflower
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, bike, car, roller
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who growsrose is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Flower    | orchid | rose          | poppy    | bellflower | begonia  |
| Transport   | bike  | roller | quad-bike | car | bus |

