.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, july, april, may, march
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, pumpkin, grapefruit, garlic, peas
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Birthday   | april | december      | may | july | march |
| Food     | garlic  | pumpkin | asparagus     | peas     | grapefruit  |

