.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
City: rome, new-york, miami, berlin, marseilles
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing, collecting, hiking, gardening
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| City      | marseilles | miami | rome      | berlin | new-york      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | hiking       | baking | gardening  | collecting |

