4. the fan of blues is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
