.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, board-games, reading-climbing, reading
5 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, bird, hedgehog, mouse
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading-climbing is the owner of the bird##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Hobby   | gardening   | board-games    | reading | reading-climbing   | drawing |
| Pet     | ferret | frog | hedgehog | bird | mouse    |

