.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There 5 different types of food: eggplant, peas, grapefruit, cucumber, mango
5 different games are played: go, whist, monopoly, backgammon, billiard
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Food   | mango     | grapefruit       | eggplant     | peas  | cucumber  |
| Game      | backgammon | go | whist | billiard | monopoly |

