.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
House: craftsman, colonial, modern, ranch-style, palace
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, rock, reggae, r&b
1. the fan of techno is in the middle##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the modern house is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| House   | colonial | palace | modern | craftsman | ranch-style |
| Music-Genre           | r&b | reggae  | techno    | dubstep  | rock   |

 